{"tid":853931,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"G奶女神共浴21歲外甥17年　苦笑「這很普遍」","createTime":"2018-10-09T03:37:50.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-11T12:46:19.000Z","uid":72009,"like":212,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":73,"replies":[{"pid":"4b4bb3851e317ff9fa2df3aeba895522b7fda3e8","tid":853931,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T03:37:50.000Z","msg":"「早安少女組」33歲前成員後藤真希外型甜美，擁有G罩杯好身材，看不出已是2個孩子的媽。她日前帶21歲演員外甥勸修寺保都上節目，自爆在他17歲前都一起洗澡，嚇壞眾人。她前天出席新書《現在的我》（暫譯）發行活動，提到共浴話題，她苦笑說：「這在後藤家很普遍。」<br />\n<br />\n她前天現身東京的新書發行活動，被問到與勸修寺保都共浴17年，她無奈表示，身為住在同個屋簷下的阿姨，「我從姊姊的小孩（勸修寺）喝奶時期就一直在一起，如果對方沒有拒絕就一起入浴，這在後藤家很普遍」，但也笑說：「姊夫不會加入。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20181009/640_7a8c53631d489f19bc2e327b97b163bc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20181009%2F640_7a8c53631d489f19bc2e327b97b163bc.jpg&h=8e1e14c3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/recommend/realtime/20181009/1444185\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Frecommend%2Frealtime%2F20181009%2F1444185&d=sZljDrWenY9hBEOu%2BnkSMy7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=02bf2a2f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Frecommend%2Frealtime%2F20181009%2F1444185&h=ebfb856b\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/recommend/realtime/20181009/1444185</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一定好硬"},{"pid":"97eb6502f3dd622c5f6319b370e67ee022ee9eea","tid":853931,"uid":37281,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T03:40:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0f70e0edd26920e78b254e7a8eba4e35707b0a02","tid":853931,"uid":72009,"like":101,"dislike":0,"score":101,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T03:41:56.000Z","msg":"姊夫加入，2對1，很忙"},{"pid":"f26bbdb475e3f5289cf5abf057d933bda41550bc","tid":853931,"uid":122134,"like":215,"dislike":1,"score":214,"citedBy":0,"reply